      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a buyer looking for dependable basic transportation or a practical project. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who appreciates an honest, no-frills car at an accessible price point. A great opportunity to get into a vehicle without stretching your budget.",
