    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right owner? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and could make a great cheap commuter, first project, or handy spare to have around. A straightforward, honest little car at a sensible price \u2014 ideal for someone who sees value where others just see age. If you want something affordable and usable without spending a fortune, it\u2019s well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong-running powertrain feel and honest, utilitarian character. This car shows its age cosmetically and needs some sorting, but it still offers dependable core mechanicals, a willing engine, and a drivetrain that makes it worth saving. Great candidate for someone who knows their way around maintenance, wants an affordable commuter, or is looking for a platform to refresh over time. Priced to reflect condition while leaving room for the next owner to add value.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
