      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, lived-in character you can feel the moment you see it\u2014a no-nonsense driver with plenty of story left to write. It\u2019s the perfect fit for someone who appreciates a budget-friendly ride with real project potential, whether you need simple transportation, a practical backup, or a weekend tinkering companion. There\u2019s a rugged charm here that makes it stand out from the forgettable crowd, and at this price, it\u2019s an accessible way to get behind the wheel of something with personality.",
